===Etymology===
Graphical manipulations on {{l|cmn|兵|tr=bīng||soldier}}, converting it into a similar-sounding onomatopoeia. First attested in {{w|Qing Dynasty}} and referred to the sound of collisions (during a fight). Later used as a translation of English {{term|ping pong|lang=en}}.

